    <item>
      <title>特朗普呼吁为美国国土导弹防御系统部署“铁穹”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-calls-for-iron-dome-for-us-homeland-missile-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统正在准备一项行政命令，以部署“下一代”防御系统，保护美国免受弹道导弹和其他远程攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-calls-for-iron-dome-for-us-homeland-missile-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 17:31:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普准备禁止跨性别军队入伍，恢复因新冠而退伍的士兵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-to-reinstate-troops-discharged-for-refusing-covid-vaccine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统唐纳德·特朗普将签署行政命令，限制跨性别军人在军队服役，并恢复因拒绝接种新冠疫苗而被退伍的人员的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-to-reinstate-troops-discharged-for-refusing-covid-vaccine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 15:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚总统武契奇寻求政府改组以平息大规模抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/protesters-rally-in-serbia-s-capital-in-challenge-to-vucic-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚总统亚历山大·武契奇呼吁更换至少一半的政府部长，以平息因火车站屋顶倒塌事故引发的近三个月的抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/protesters-rally-in-serbia-s-capital-in-challenge-to-vucic-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 15:29:59 GMT</pubDate>
